@startuml
title Radiotherapy Workflow – Simulation Saga

hide empty description

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam Shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F4F6F8
  BorderColor #5A6473
  FontSize 11
  ArrowFontSize 9
  ArrowColor #444444
}

[*] --> ARTCreated

state "1. ART Workflow Start" as SIM {
  state ARTCreated
  state SimSubmitted
  state SimInProgress
  state SimCompleted
  state ImageStored
}

state Cancelled #FFC0CB : ◎ terminal

' ─── Transitions ─────────────────────────
ARTCreated--> SimSubmitted: SIM-001 SubmitSimulationRequest [User]\n«Physician»
SimSubmitted--> SimInProgress : SIM-002 StartSimulation [Sys]
SimInProgress --> SimCompleted : SIM-003 SubmitSimulationRecord [User]\n«SimTech»
SimCompleted --> ImageStored: SIM-004 CheckDailyImgAndReferencePlan [Sys]
SimSubmitted--> Cancelled : SIM-005 CancelCase [User]\n«Physician»
SimInProgress --> Cancelled : SIM-005 CancelCase [User]\n«Physician»
SimCompleted --> Cancelled : SIM-005 CancelCase [User]\n«Physician»
@enduml